Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.63,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Malam Biru pun dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:05.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wujudmu sungguh mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:10.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri? Kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:14.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:18.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:28.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu pergi dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:33.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasa sakit dari menanggung\Nkekuatan yang besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,ketergantungan terhadap\Nyang bersifat material.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:42.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham penderitaan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persis seperti diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:50.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang tetap di sisiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:59.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asalkan ada dirimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidak butuh apa-apa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mencin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang dia lakukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:27.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa, Yuri? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:31.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu mengkhianatiku, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:35.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kubunuh kamu!\NDasar ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:50.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persis seperti diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar sialan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kilatan biru tadi itu apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menghubungi kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:20.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini sudah waktunya tidur.\NSegera ke kasur kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepala Biara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepala Biara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hukuman langit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Eminescu! Selamatkan dirimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal tinggal sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Michaela, kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Larilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Igor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:58.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Pergi dan tinggalkan aku saja!\N- Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:08.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah! Apa yang terjadi?\NBawakan pemadam api!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada Homare di sini!\NCepat lakukan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di kediaman utama ribut sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia sedang berguncang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh! Tubuh!\NTubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:36.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tatsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Tatsuma, selamatkan dirimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,On! Nisomuba basaraun hatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:52.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dingin, dingin tapi tubuhku
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,terbakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nekosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah semua pertanda ini\Nmenuju ke hal ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar, para anak muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:10.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Evakuasi keluarga kuil\Nke kaki gunung dengan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:11.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takezo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:17.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu yang memimpin mereka!\NLalu lepaskan Yamantaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan membantu Tuan Tatsuma.\NAku mengandalkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga dirimu juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu, Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan ikut para anak muda\Nuntuk turun gunung.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:39.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gampang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian memang anak-anak yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakakmu ini akan melindungi kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoshi, sini pegangan ke pundakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa, Nyonya Torako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau terjadi sesuatu padamu dan anakmu,\Nnanti bisa dimarahi Nekosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, Ryuuji juga bilang iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakiku sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beratnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:26.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Renzou, sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon!\NBiarkan mereka istirahat sebentar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mengeluh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita disuruh untuk turun gunung\Nsecepat mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar anak manja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada api biru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bocah kurang ajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada laporan dari seluruh negeri\Ntentang meningkatnya keganasan iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya familiar\Njadi sulit dikendalikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini ada hubungannya\Ndengan pembunuhan bayi Satan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau jangan bilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Armumahel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Azazel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ja-Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan, Lewin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lepaskan, Osceola!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:53.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat!\NMungkin ini rasukan paksa dari Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyonya Shemihaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beliau bertahan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:10.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satan mulai bergentayangan mencari wadah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ilya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:13.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa Shiemi ke tempat berlindung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai terjadi sesuatu\Npada anak di kandungannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aria sudah tidak efektif, mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para Doctor mencoba membawa Yuri Egin pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cih, malah di saat sibuk begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan mereka.\NMasih ada satu lagi di dalam perutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mereka melawan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Palladion, Arc Knight siap bertempur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wanita dan anak di dalam kandungannya\Nhanya manusia biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami akan melakukan operasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:04.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada buktinya!\NKami diperintah membunuh kedua anaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi, kalau terus begini, ibunya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:10.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti juga ada jalannya!\NYang penting anaknya mati dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:14.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, sepertinya dia sudah sekarat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:17.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik langsung dibunuh\Ndan masalah pun selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa-apaan kamu?\NSudah gila, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru kalianlah yang harus\Ndinginkan kepala dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum ada perintah membunuh Egin.\NKalau seenaknya lagi, aku tembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pengkhianat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:35.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan! Beliau hanya mematuhi\Nperintah Grigori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:40.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri, apa kamu mendengarku?\NKalau terus begini, kamu akan dibunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lahirkan dia kalau ingin hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:51.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya istirahat sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:52.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Colada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ulmodo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gintora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu cepat dan gesit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus! Sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah lahir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mati suri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segera bawa ke ruang tindakan NICU!\NKalau tidak cepat, akan terlambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:06.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak itu tidak boleh pergi dari sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:10.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kami yang memastikan\Ndia mewarisi kekuatan Satan atau tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada waktu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sama sekali tidak bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu, coba rangsang dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:19.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik! Tidak ada reaksi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:30.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Periksa warna matanya!\NKalau bersinar biru, berarti anaknya Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mata kanannya berwarna hijau normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:38.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bisa mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku yang memastikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:51.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kumohon, serahkan anak itu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada celah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:08.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kena! Ini saatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus, Loxley!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Napasnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kasihan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:21.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bernapas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingin memeluknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maxima Fuego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enkerei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru muncul sekarang, badut sialan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin telah gugur,\Nberarti Operasi Petir Biru sudah gagal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai sekarang, biar aku yang ambil alih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:34.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian para Doctor sudah tidak dibutuhkan,\Nsilakan mundur dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai Doctor,\Naku hanya bisa mengatakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mendoakan keberuntunganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:45.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, dia sehat walafiat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa rencanamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihatlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:08.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan pedang Paladin, Tizona pun tidak bisa\Nmenghancurkan jantung anak Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku melawannya secara langsung,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:15.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,dampaknya akan menjadi bencana\Nyang lebih besar dari saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:17.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan pedang itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukannya ini tidak ada isinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:31.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku membuat pedang itu\Nseratus lima puluh tahun yang lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu memberikannya pada biksu muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percaya saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:42.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula tidak ada yang tahu\Ncara mengalahkan anaknya Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi aku hanya melakukan sebisaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:49.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mundurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasang pertahanan yang paling kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikatlah kebenaran sebagai sabuk,\Nkenakan keadilan sebagai pelindung dada,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:02.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,doa sebagai helm,\Nkeimanan sebagai perisai,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan genggamlah pedang roh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:07.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan melawannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:16.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia hanya melindungi\Nkita dan dirinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku bersamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian pergilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:40.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya bisa beraksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, sarungnya juga berharga, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Zeuxo, plexaura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cerceis, plouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Europa, eudora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku memohon kepada...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga Ribu Putri Istana Oceanus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:51.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oceanids Carousel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bocah tidur saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jantungnya
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyerap ke pedang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, pedang ini semacam\Npintu ke mana saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:19.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gagangnya terhubung ke Gehenna,\Ndan sarungnya menjadi pintu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:24.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketika keduanya bersatu,\Nbisa menyegel iblis Gehenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, setelah menyegel jantungnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia jadi terpisah dari sifat iblisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya menjadi manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:46.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bayi ini tetap manusia dan iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:49.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik bunuh saja selagi dia anteng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama jantungnya belum dihancurkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia akan terus bangkit kembali\Nmeskipun kita membunuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:20:00.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, segel hanyalah sebatas segel.\NPasti ada batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:05.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam situasi ini, kita hanya bisa mengurung\Ntubuhnya secara semi-permanen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan terus menghancurkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia juga manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:17.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepribadian macam apa yang akan terbentuk\Ndari manusia yang terus-menerus disiksa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:22.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ingin melahirkan\NSatan dan Lucifer yang kedua?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bermaksud...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi mencegah hal itu, lebih baik
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:40.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita mengembalikannya ke pelukan ibunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Pheles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:56.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik jangan berterima kasih padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musuh baru telah muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:05.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api biru?\NBukankah jantungnya sudah disegel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan ulah bayinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:08.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:28.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Ayah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:44.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Tubuh ini boleh juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:55.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata kamu ada di sini
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:03.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menemukanmu, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:08.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
